'''Screamer Squadron''' was one of hundreds of fighter units created during the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic's]] recovery during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. The squadron used [[X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wing starfighters]].

==History==
As a significant percentage of experienced New Republic pilots were killed or badly injured during the first few years of the war, there was a large shortage of pilots to lead these new units, for example, [[Barefoot Squadron]] led by a sixteen year old [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]]. Such was the case with Screamer Squadron, which was led by a twenty three year old pilot who was by no means a veteran.

Screamer Squadron flew X-wing starfighters when it took part in the [[Battle of Ylesia (28 ABY)|botched mission]] against the [[Peace Brigade]] Government of the [[Cha Raaba system|Ylesia system]].

